GHI 2009 Income (group data)

Source: R/data.R
gd_GHI_2009_income.Rd

A dataset containing national group data for the fake country GHI for the year 2009. Income based welfare values.

gd_GHI_2009_income

Format

A data frame with 10 rows and 5 variables:

country_code

A fake three letter country code.

survey_year

The year of the survey.

weight

The weight of each indvidual's welfare value.

welfare

The welfare of each indvidual. Can represent either income or consumption.

area

Geographical location; urban or rural.

Source

Worldbank internal.

Details

Note that nothing in this dataset is real. It is only meant for testing and example purposes.
